description:
This week on Unqualified, Anna and Sim sit down with Colin Hanks (THE HOUSE BUNNY, KING KONG, LIFE IN PIECES) to chat about working on teen movies and avoiding type-casting (9:52) and play some Deal-Breakers! (23:45)

Later they play a round of House Bunny trivia (56:05), then call Bridget (1:06:00) who's starting a relationship podcast and wants to know how much she should reveal about something in her past. Tune in!
